title: friend_pre
---
<<set $context = "intimate">>

You've known each other for a long time. This feels like crossing a line.

-> $c2: "Are you sure about this?"
    <<set $tone = "careful">>
    <<jump friend_start>>

-> $c2: "I've wanted this for a while."
    <<set $tone = "honest">>
    <<jump friend_start>>

-> $c2: Stay quiet, just look at them
    <<set $tone = "vulnerable">>
    <<jump friend_start>>
===

title: friend_start
---
They take a breath, then move closer.

<<fade_out>>
<<jump friend_act>>
===

title: friend_act
---
Everything feels more intense. Familiar, but different.

-> $c2: Focus on them completely
    <<set $sync += 2>>
    <<set $presence += 2>>
    "You notice every small reaction."

-> $c2: Get lost in the moment
    <<set $sync += 1>>
    <<set $presence += 1>>
    "You stop thinking, just feeling."

-> $c2: Hold back slightly
    <<set $sync -= 1>>
    <<set $presence += 0>>
    "Something feels restrained."

-> $c2: Say their name softly
    <<set $sync += 1>>
    <<set $presence += 2>>
    "They respond immediately."

===

title: friend_post
---
<<fade_in>>

Silence, but not empty.

-> $c2: "Did that change things?"
    <<set $emotional_outcome += 1>>
    "They smile, uncertain but warm."

-> $c2: "We can pretend this didn't happen."
    <<set $emotional_outcome -= 2>>
    "That lands badly."

-> $c2: Just stay with them quietly
    <<set $emotional_outcome += 2>>
    "They lean closer."

===
